[SN]TITLE[SN]
50 Cent says rapping teacher Just Muz 'got some flow'

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
Global rap superstar 50 Cent has said a teacher rapping to his pupils has "got some flow".

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
50 Cent shared a video of teacher Christian Foley with the 37.9m people who like his Facebook page.
In the video pupils whoop and cheer as he shows off his verbal gymnastics in the educational rap, rhyming words like angles and ratio.
Mr Foley, who goes by the rap name Just Muz, said: "It's been absolutely crazy, I mean 50 Cent!"
